### 1. Get Token (Authentication)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth-token/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "testpassword"
}

### 2. Get all books (should work without auth - AllowAny)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/books/
Accept: application/json

### 3. Try to create book WITHOUT token (should fail - 401 Unauthorized)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/books_all/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Unauthorized Book",
    "author": "Anonymous"
}

### 4. Create book WITH token (replace {token} with actual token from step 1)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/books_all/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token {your-token-here}

{
    "title": "Authenticated Book",
    "author": "Authenticated Author"
}

### 5. Get books from ViewSet (requires auth)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/books_all/
Authorization: Token {your-token-here}
Accept: application/json

### 6. Update a book (requires auth)
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/books_all/1/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token {your-token-here}

{
    "title": "Updated Authenticated Book",
    "author": "Updated Author"
}

### 7. Delete a book (requires auth)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/books_all/1/
Authorization: Token {your-token-here}